data.description: Beautiful ALMOST NEW 3/2/2 home built in 2021!  Great lot ~ 1.16 acre in Rolling Hills!  OPEN FLOOR PLAN with vaulted ceilings and spacious rooms. Eat-in kitchen has large breakfast bar, SS appliances, and pantry.  Split bedrooms.  Master suite has TWO closets and ensuite with walk-in shower and water closet.  Inside laundry room.  Pretty views from every window! No HOA.  Peaceful and private lot with no neighbors on either side.  SOLAR PANELS included ~ low electric bill!  Minutes from SR 200 shopping, dining, medical, parks, and close to World Equestrian Center also!
